{"tid":1992231,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"涉及縱火燒大埔警署及牛頭角向警淋腐液 三少年獲高院批准保釋","createTime":"2020-04-28T04:38:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-28T09:07:53.000Z","uid":240362,"like":32,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"bd4bf155a6fadf81a65341ce229d6c3fdadf81f8","tid":1992231,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T04:38:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200428/LJWJXSB5MT3ETN4SBGPAB2KGQY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200428%2FLJWJXSB5MT3ETN4SBGPAB2KGQY%2F&d=mbsn9%2Fi9gU9wZYjOUdyYPhjXlokmAnOoGQHL1SEg040%3D&h=e433c8c9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200428%2FLJWJXSB5MT3ETN4SBGPAB2KGQY%2F&h=a51d0281\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200428/LJWJXSB5MT3ETN4SBGPAB2KGQY/</a><br />\n<br />\n摘要: 大埔警署本月初遭人投擲汽油彈熏黑，警方事後拘捕兩名18歲學生，控以縱火等罪，兩人提堂後不准保釋；另一名16歲少年則被指上月在牛頭角住所向警員投擲懷疑通渠水，被控為造成他人身體嚴重傷害而淋腐蝕性物品罪，同樣不准保釋。三人還押多時，今早分別向高等法院申請保釋，獲法官潘兆童批准，得以繼續學業及工作。"},{"pid":"5d6361949cdee70416d2eda69dc5278208c2ec0d","tid":1992231,"uid":32473,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T04:39:47.000Z","msg":"唉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11dac14910391e225b12a71f4c13037798bd28f4","tid":1992231,"uid":328890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T04:43:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c09d0c6d3514eed1ff36cae864bc4a92e186eec3","tid":1992231,"uid":44358,"like":9,"dislike":5,"score":4,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T05:25:53.000Z","msg":"自從紅官單嘢爆出嚟後，其他官唔敢再玩嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aaaeb4ec93ab919c87da80b8ca18849b6b6747df","tid":1992231,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5d6361949cdee70416d2eda69dc5278208c2ec0d","tid":1992231,"uid":32473,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-